{"tid":2233854,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林卓廷首仗勝何君堯","createTime":"2020-10-07T12:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T14:06:10.000Z","uid":296589,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7783d2598583bc1a60d3e5f21b899a023c854781","tid":2233854,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"轉載林卓延廷fb<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/534865589914032/posts/3343783772355519/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F534865589914032%2Fposts%2F3343783772355519%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=bcb831d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/534865589914032/posts/3343783772355519/</a><br />\n<br />\n【告何君堯 首仗報捷！！ 】<br />\n林卓廷就721告何君堯誹謗案今日第一堂，何君堯由於未有回應涉嫌誹謗言論的事實根據等資料，最終法庭指令佢需於14日內回應我方眾多提問，包括有何事實根據指721當日林卓廷喺西環帶幾百人入元朗搞事，法庭同時命令何君堯負責今堂訟費。"},{"pid":"0da4836b3c4de4d1fe4d512837e62c43b06f70d3","tid":2233854,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"最好有証據何妖煽動白衣人"},{"pid":"66ae1aca6bd5bd4f247ea6c6dc90307c8b7ab468","tid":2233854,"uid":296589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532eb558f9ba986673191814e37677581f611032","tid":2233854,"uid":78768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:59:27.000Z","msg":"林卓廷：贏緊5:0<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n律政司介入&gt;撤控&gt;完"},{"pid":"b4be965de1aad53a0d6678